            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Ability to find requirements quickly when you need them&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Avoid unnecessary development work through better prioritization and alignment with requirements&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Avoid having to manually establish and maintain traceability&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Reduce effort related to requirements change&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Increase documentation team efficiency&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Improve Quality &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Reduction of defects at each stage (Pre-Implementation, Pre-Release, Post-Release)&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Increase Value &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
